column4: Text

NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "8639D5294C1AFE5A10379488D8D9CB68", "This stinking hole is full of goblins that raided our forward camp.

The gobs are led by some big goblin boss named "Wideload."
Get in there and make him pay!")
NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "7F50FDEF477B8C5B98DEB0A5F6A1423F", "Well done. That\'s a good choice of gear. You look much more capable.")

NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "0090B2E142E9DC39928D2A9993B324D5", "Welcome, adventurer! You're here just in time.

We're recovering from a goblin raid — they slaughtered our soldiers and stole our gear.

Kill those goblins, gear up with what you find and meet me outside the Den of Upheaval.

We don't have much time. Go!")
NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "F07B875A4DE434309AE96BA6A0354E1A", "Hi, can I help you with something?")
NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "5CCF13A34922A4480F95508BE0017D27", "Why don\'t I ever get patrol duty?")

NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "81FD943F44DD95AEDA1F75A9CD34748F", "Going after the greenskins, are you?\r\n\r\nI don\'t envy you. Our corporal was part of the spelunking division - says there\'s one out there who enjoys making flatcakes out of human flesh.")

NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "F0F311FB49A4497C83ADE5B4BE916DA4", "I've heard you're making some good progress out there. You'll make even more progress if you gain some new skills.

Slay the monsters that live in the woods, collect <span color="#FFD700">Skill Points</> and <span color="#FFD700">Gold</>. You'll need them to upgrade your <span color="#FFD700">Skill Station</>.

We'll speak again when the tasks are finished.")
NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "F3B0155A4B515D6BB265499888784F96", "The resources you gathered will be useful to establish yourself in your new fort.\r\n\r\nI feel like you\'re ready for the next step…")

NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "A20C42574930D315325CED86521EEDF0", "Pass through the <span color=\"#FFD700\">portal</> here in town and go to your <span color=\"#FFD700\">fort</>. There you\'ll meet with an <span color=\"#FFD700\">Imperial liason</> and learn how to advance your skills as you make your new home your own.")

NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "CDAA86B44284E2B31609308BF76FC523", "Oh, great, our \"mighty\" hero arrives. Here\'s your fort — such as it is. As per our agreement according to the Frontiers accord, this fort is yours to do with as you choose.\r\n\r\nYou\'ll want to take my advice though: you\'ll need a <span color=\"#FFD700\">Skill Station</> to focus on improving your skills. You\'ll need to keep improving yourself to survive in the frontiers.")

NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "4709CAD6493B9DF257FA66879EB3EB1E", "I hope you got something useful from your Skill Station, because after this, you're on your own.

Keep honing your skills. You won't be able to help us defeat the netherim if you're dead.

Make sure you actually use the skills you've learned and you just might make it.")

NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "30B905F8456FF6FD32C495A21AFD5308", "Interesting arrangement. Ahem, I suppose you can always move them later. Anyway, take this surplus of logs to make some <span color=\"#FFD700\">planks</> before we move on to the next step.")

NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "E84DC1AF4F78E6314321FBAE79E2EBC0", "Great. Now that you\'ve got a Relic Weapon, you\'re ready to really mix it up with the goblins. We keep clearing this cave out, but it keeps filling up with goblins.\r\n\r\nGrab your Relic Weapon, head in, clear it out, and meet me back here.")

NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "4971F6FF4AE039E870D860AD1F03B486", "Well done. I\'m not sure how long that cave will remain empty, but thanks for helping. These woods teem with goblins and I don\'t have enough men to go \'round. I\'ll need you to take care of some things for me before you can move on.")

NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "BD47C373472DADEF852C219E6C85B8C0", "Yeesh. Sorry. If you haven\'t started itching yet, it won\'t be long. There\'s some sort of illness spreading across everyone in the Outpost. Yapper gave me a list of ingredients for an antidote. I\'m skeptical, but at this point, I just want to stop scratching. Please, bring me these ingredients!")
NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "E70306534565B8D891703392EC5D8EDD", "Finally! I\'m going to just throw this all together. This had better work.")

NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "7DF19E9541FDD28C22F209AAA66D38E1", "Hey, hero. You were a big help defending the outpost from the goblins. We took the head raider captive and it turns out he can actually talk. In fact, now that he's recovering, it's tough to get him to shut up. He seems pretty eager to sell out the rest of his kind.

I hope you’re ready to help because we’ve been having trouble with a rather large and angry goblin called <span color="#FFD700">Wideload</>. You’re not going to be of any use with the meager belongings you’ve brought, so let’s go get some better stuff for you. These goblins play with fire, so you'll need some fire resistant armor. Here, you're gonna need this potion, too.

Go get everything on this <span color="#FFD700">list of gear</>, then meet me outside the <span color="#FFD700">Den of Upheaval</>.")

NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "FBAE42BE40AE64CDA1C8A1B3E9B3B45A", "Head towards the guarded gate to my left and follow the path beyond the two banners to get to <span color=\"#FFD700\">Wood\'s Edge</>.")

NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "5F2C545549C3EEA6FA6EFEB9F46362D0", "That's what I like to see, a fully kitted-out frontierlander.

The Emperor wants all of you prepared to face the gobs, so they've authorized me to give you a <span color="#FFD700">Relic Weapon</>. Relic Weapons grow stronger while you carry them in battle, even if you're not wielding them.

We keep clearing this cave out, but it keeps filling up with goblins. Grab your Relic Weapon, clear it out, and meet me back here.")
NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "F656A30649CCFAA2993AA39E8C5430E9", "I told you to meet me outside of the <span color=\"#FFD700\">Den of Upheaval</>. I\'ve got a favor to ask of you there.")

NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "407A73914F7AB96487741994E4569550", "You\'re doing pretty well, but beyond Wood\'s Edge there are tougher, grizzlier goblins. You\'ll need even <span color=\"#FFD700\">better armor</> and <span color=\"#FFD700\">weapons</>.")

NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "374C076B41FD175B16C9F59CBE9EAC25", "Aggh, somebody turn that down. You hear that, right?

Anyway, I’m looking for an intrepid explorer who can brave these dangerous lands to procure for me the fabled <span color="#FFD700">Embershine</>!

You get it and I’ll pay ya.")

NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "B5F625BE44FEE5139D238CBAA4638293", "You found it? Yeah, that’s the stuff! Glows like spark ember and burns like flame ember. Here’s some of my old stuff I had lying around.")

NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "96DFF4F44D44FBEBD7F0DA90EC4E08FE", "These idiot gobs are pretty much pushovers.

They've got some <span color="#FFD700">brutes</> that are giving us a bit more trouble though.

Bring me their <span color="#FFD700">shields</> and we'll show 'em who's in charge.")

NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "9B89909A435ABFECC22836AF38D31FCC", "That\'ll show ‘em! Our engineers finished their little art project. Go check it out in front of the outpost.\r\n\r\nLet those brutes look at this the next time they consider giving you any trouble.")

NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "7950D9094CDBEB5DA5FEE7A6C011D429", "Hey there, buddy! Hey, hey! Listen, listen. Listen.\r\nLast time the Imps hired me to do their dirty work here, some of these knuckleheads kicked the bucket while they had some of my schtufff.\r\nIf you go get my schtuff back, I’ll make it worth yer while...")

NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "FFB9188043D10909A84CC5BC0267D2B2", "Aw yeah, that’s the schtuff! Had to get yer hands dirty, didja? Them rats get pretty fat on them corpses, eh? Here’s a little somethin’ ta help ya not become one of them! Har, har har!")

NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "86C2B659487DA333E5BC578778E6EB85", "Yapper knows where goblins keepin' humen prisoners.
But Yapper cold! Maybe you help Yapper out and Yapper tell you where humens is.

Filthy <span color="#FFD700">mossrats</> make dirty messes, but goblins know, those messes burn real long time. Yapper teach you ol' goblin trick, you keep fires burning long time.

You go get sum <span color="#FFD700">mossrat nuggets</>, bring 'em back to Yapper and Yapper tell you where tasty humens is.")

NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "A03605F54356EE7C6A0030B33500FB43", "Ah! Yeah, yeah! That the stuff. Snnnnif! Good and strong!\r\nOkay, you. Big goblin Wideload lock up humens in Lost Woods. Big humen boss know where that at.")

NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "3733CEFE46F7936811315D8EA316515A", "Hmn… Yapper hungry. Yapper told humens about tasty Broiled Pigfish. They don\'t believe Yapper that it taste just like pig! Yapper knows, though. Yapper has secret fishin\' spot and knows what Pigfish eat. You go get Pigfish, I let you eat some, too!")
NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "A98876E9491E7D6FCBDEAFB5FE1DCA97", "Yum! That\'s the fish! Wait until humens taste this. It\'ll be a real surprise. Heh. Here, you have one too!")

NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "E1C035AF4BE0347A1850278D3828AA6D", "If you've wandered into the forest at night, you must've met the <span color="#FFD700">zombies</>. They clearly weren't goblins, so where did these people come from?

There are records of a group of colonists that took shelter in a nearby cave, but were never heard from again.

If you <span color="#FFD700">bring me some of their clothing</>, I can confirm their origins.")
NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "E32B17AD4CE0B9823B042E8A5A681340", "The Netherim has been controlling the Hyvid Queen? I can\'t imagine what else they\'ve managed to get their maws on. ")

NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "1509A48544620DD80CB651B253A51E55", "How goes the spelunking? If I failed to mention it before, you can find the <span color=\"#FFD700\">Cave of Sorrows</> located within <span color=\"#FFD700\">Wood\'s Edge</>.")

NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "C82379964E9BE07DE1B7E6AA5B21A510", "Ugh. Thanks for …ulp, bringing these to me. I\'ll study these and find out where these people are from. Man, I wish I knew a stink removal spell.")
NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "D33263654F056DA2C9CC6B8279532705", "Just killing the goblins isn\'t enough.\r\n\r\nWe need to ruin their lives, give \'em hell every day, in every way.")
NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "26E364BB4DFA54A40F28B19AC80CFF8C", "I recommend activating this waypoint before you venture any further.")

NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "95CEECDB485C189FE1817CA4F50D6283", "With this many Scrolls of the Damned, you should be able to enter the Dead\'s End. You\'ll have to fight your way there through the undead, so make sure you clear out a bunch of them.\r\n\r\nHead in there, kill the skull lord and take back the weapon.")

NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "6980BA1D49B36EBCD66AB487B54F5201", "You did it! The Skull Lord was a formidable foe.

The weapon you retrieved is ideal for cutting your way into goblin territory. It's yours, you've earned it.

Well done.")

NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "613BF4D74B3EBE52E364139835CF0F3F", "Make your way to <span color=\"#FFD700\">Lake Gobdunk</>, where you will also find the entrance to the <span color=\"#FFD700\">Restless Glade</>.")

NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "9E354CE047AB77C1E903558C348352FF", "The <span color=\"#FFD700\">Restless Glade</> is located somewhere around <span color=\"#FFD700\">Lake Gobdunk</>, but the further you venture away from the Imperial Outpost, the more challenging it will be to survive without proper training. I hope you are ready for this.")

NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "C4CFBA874193963B4CDD1BADCD20BB7D", "You want Yapper to tell you about man-mashers? Oh, Yapper knows. Yapper knows all about dem.

You give Yapper tasty snacks if Yapper tells you, yes? Oh yes. Greenies dragged them from <span color="#FFD700">Snotskin Village</> into a cave.

You can find, yes?")

NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "A053A3A34D694EA77CB7CABC5F716EA2", "Make your way through the <span color=\"#FFD700\">Well-Trodden Path</> from the <span color=\"#FFD700\">Imperial Battlefield</> to get to <span color=\"#FFD700\">Snotskin Village</>.")

NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "77E6476E4F4F6CD4E828EAAF11F31615", "Those siege weapons are stashed somewhere in <span color=\"#FFD700\">Snotskin Village</>, and I need you to go find that <span color=\"#FFD700\">Goblin Stash</> as soon as possible.")

NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "72CBC5A5407FE196ACE263B5151F99D4", "Those siege weapons are stashed somewhere in <span color=\"#FFD700\">Snotskin Village</>, and I need you to go find that <span color=\"#FFD700\">Goblin Stash</> as soon as possible.")

NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "7EF65C7D4B8BAA2F33BCC79AF3B304D0", "Word has it that the gobs have \"improved\" our stolen imperial siege weapons. They\'ve even coined ridiculous new names for them, like the <span color=\"#FFD700\">Smash Blaster</>, <span color=\"#FFD700\">Sword-o-Matic</>, and <span color=\"#FFD700\">Man Tenderizer</>. \r\n\r\nHead to the <span color=\"#FFD700\">Snotskin Village</> and destroy these weapons from their <span color=\"#FFD700\">Goblin Stash</> before the weapons can be used against us.")

NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "78509C70497ED201463372BD626CD758", "Word has it that the gobs have \"improved\" our stolen imperial siege weapons. They\'ve even coined ridiculous new names for them, like the <span color=\"#FFD700\">Smash Blaster</>, <span color=\"#FFD700\">Sword-o-Matic</>, and <span color=\"#FFD700\">Man Tenderizer</>. \r\n\r\nHead to the <span color=\"#FFD700\">Snotskin Village</> and destroy these weapons from their <span color=\"#FFD700\">Goblin Stash</> before the weapons can be used against us.")

NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "E6F968074E7B3A1365B625ACCF8AE238", "Word has it that the gobs have \"improved\" our stolen imperial siege weapons. They\'ve even coined ridiculous new names for them, like the <span color=\"#FFD700\">Smash Blaster</>, <span color=\"#FFD700\">Sword-o-Matic</>, and <span color=\"#FFD700\">Man Tenderizer</>. \r\n\r\nHead to the <span color=\"#FFD700\">Snotskin Village</> and destroy these weapons from their <span color=\"#FFD700\">Goblin Stash</> before the weapons can be used against us.")

NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "B2DCF91344811583C1EF83811BF73CE3", "Yes, yes, <span color=\"#FFD700\">Mancake Maker</> is big goblin. You smash Mancake Maker, not Yapper, okay? You find Mancake Maker in <span color=\"#FFD700\">Goblin Stash</>. You smash him good for Yapper.")

NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "035C048D4EAF8CAE0A0178A6F7402B61", "Nice work taking out those repurposed siege weapons.

Who knows if the gobs would have ever gotten them working, but we'd better not take the chance.

They're stupid, but dangerous.")

NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "56771C564822FD3872AE548DFC969742", "We've gotten reports of a powerful weapon we could use to defeat the goblins.

Unfortunately, there's a section of the forest near the goblin village overrun with the undead. This is where the weapon is and the undead have erected a magical barrier to protect it.

The captain of one of our previous expeditions was secretly dabbling in dark forces. When overrun by goblins, he led a retreat to the caves where he tried to hold the gobs off by raising members of his expedition as they fell.

If there's something we can use to gain access to the <span color="#FFD700">Dead's End</>, that's where we'll find it. We need any advantage we can get.")

NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "068E028849BABF76845A149620907359", "The <span color=\"#FFD700\">Ostian Sepulcher</> within <span color=\"#FFD700\">Snotskin Village</> is crawling with the undead. If you are looking for <span color=\"#FFD700\">Scrolls of the Damned</>, the <span color=\"#FFD700\">undead</> are sure to carry them--but be careful when toying with dark magic. You might find some unpleasant surprises the further you dig.")

NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "FDDDC7E1452138C00D6309BB42FB1E25", "Zaya\'s opinion may differ, but <span color=\"#FFD700\">Dast</> was once a great <span color=\"#FFD700\">Imperial Captain</>. Perhaps you can find his remains in the <span color=\"#FFD700\">Ostian Sepulcher</> and finally put his soul to rest.")

NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "9AEEB074440DECA262D46D976C261A46", "It\'s a shame how Dast has fallen into darkness, but at least you\'ve found the scrolls.\r\n\r\nTell <span color=\"#FFD700\">Zaya</> about your findings. ")

NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "87D043F049834EB089FEC4A0E4AFA0A5", "Ooh, Scrolls of the Damned. Yeesh. Not sure if I should even touch those, but those should do the trick.\r\n\r\nYou be careful fooling with dark magic. The trouble with necromancy is that it\'s easy to wander into the darkness, but tough to find your way back to the light.")

NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "F4E5DEB147FAA9C0F536799D613E6755", "What? That nasty gob Yapper said there are prisoners in the <span color=\"#FFD700\">Lost Woods</>? That must be our scouting party. They really should have returned by now. I don\'t know who this \"Wideload\" is, but I need you to get them back. Goblin prisoners don\'t last very long. I\'ve marked the Lost Woods on your map. Be careful.\r\n\r\nCome see me after you free them.")

NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "318A753F4298090A2BCF2284780471E4", "You can find the entrance to the <span color=\"#FFD700\">Lost Woods</> deep within <span color=\"#FFD700\">Wood\'s Edge</>. Please, rescue those guards!")

NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "DA4A31504AE36F3BA59862B39EB7E28C", "The <span color=\"#FFD700\">Lost Woods</> is located within <span color=\"#FFD700\">Wood\'s Edge</>, near the <span color=\"#FFD700\">Cave of Sorrows</>. Find and rescue those guards!")

NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "5F3DFA9E4F526A5AD766469DB482E415", "Thanks for freeing our guards.\r\nThey told me about this massive, menacing gob called Wideload.\r\nYou\'re growing stronger and more capable. Soon we\'ll make our strike against Wideload.")

NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "19528C874303101D6D8AC1A85C90C3C7", "Me? Skittish? You would be too, if you\'ve been where I\'ve been. General Graye needs your help defeating that big goblin Wideload before you can help us with the Hyvid infestation. One problem at a time, right?\r\n\r\nReturn here after you\'ve kicked Wideload in the shins.")

NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "721F6F86466EC301335E1F915DAE8790", "The Hyvid proliferation is growing. If you thought the Goblins were bad, wait until you stumble upon an entire swarm of Hyvid. You\'ll want to stock up on poison gear for this place.")

NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "CADE84DA46D73B19F4C962A84661A229", "Halt! I have strict orders to not let anyone into Bugswat Pass until they\'ve cleared it with Thanes Snow. You\'d better finish up everything you need to, first.")

NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "DFAF85C5426768E1A3193CABB21C30AA", "Well done! We've achieved a solid victory against the gobs.

These things keep coming out of the woodwork, so I doubt we'll ever clear them all out.

Keep your fort strong and help us hold this frontier.")
NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "6D2F1C0D4FF0EEF77B5CE8B063DE84B0", "Got word that Thanes Snow has cleared you to head in further. Good luck!")

NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "8A838A06410FC6B0319248AD7D9B2881", "It\'s about time they sent someone out here. I have reports from our Chief Imperial Guard that the outskirts of our northern encampments have been overrun by the Hyvid. Conditions are critical, and I need you to escort any of our injured guards to safety. I’m sending out reinforcements as soon as possible.\r\n\r\nThe Hyvid spew deadly poison, so you\'ll need to gather a fresh set of gear. Here\'s some to get you started.")

NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "9C121E69454A5A6DC826C7A53999ABD4", "My eyes in the forest tell me the goblins are rallying their remaining forces.\r\n\r\nThis is our chance. Assemble your team and assault the gob remnants!")
NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "DFE31E80465A712618D85BAECAFFCA06", "Harassing a guard on duty is a punishable offense under Prinicipial law.")

NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "626DC5B347FF0C1C64DE1EB88B4F64C7", "Hey! You can't move past here without approval from General Graye.

There's a village full of nasty goblins past here and the General doesn't want any more of you types wandering off, never to return again.

I'm sure if you do everything General Graye asked you to, she'll send you ahead.")
NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "05AD2D9C46E30E4C52FE3CBC3E94BE1D", "Hang on, now. The General needs your help with high priority missions.\r\n\r\nYou\'ll need to finish these quests to move ahead.")
NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "6DD04F6F4AD3697546F0F0AE625CFA3E", "It could be goosebumps, or it could be a rash.")
NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "081F625247FE8A0B58EE1EB826AEE390", "I recommend asking your physician for health advice.")
NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "8FBC1D9A45BF289734AF2A80A1BBF3F5", "Hurry along, I don\'t have time for chit-chat.")
NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "429EF9AF4850AA39F0AB9091244BD049", "Incidentally, pest control often involves dealing with more than one kind of pest.")
NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "3DEE4C8645DE2E1A649CFFAB2F89B740", "Hmn? Oh, sorry, I was in the middle of a spellbook.")
NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "0415EDE34653020F5B0152A6A6C857C4", "This is such a strange place… think of the research!")
NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "A0DB253D42EA252A611C3CAFA914D3E4", "Tell me if you find any strange ember.")
NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "2BCD7B964539DF71D40FD4A946A9193A", "Isn\'t this place amazing?")
NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "326EEB784957D03CB9CAA780F5E11983", "Hi there!")
NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "4525299A43E001D41E3D52BF3EC06863", "Yes, how can I help you?")
NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "3130BC40445C6DF9E69E98A13A46FF6E", "No, sparkle! This one\'s a friend.")
NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "B13423094BB5F2E67021D6854BACA927", "I\'m sure we can help each other.")
NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "4F52D54E440A0F1586983584670C0483", "Hey, get out there and kick some goblin butts!")
NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "20CC1D8C4C25DF291D4C5EAFDEA316C8", "Your assistance is much appreciated.")
NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "6EB2E980452CA019A5EA09A08E72ED89", "We could really use your help around here.")
NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "8818388445B8D91D4D24B0BE96C2E05C", "Hey there.")
NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "C5F8E96A4B010F6AD979C7986F564137", "Hi, can I help you with something?")
NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "CB80AEC546D2B4D5035053A3D5FDEFBD", "Hey, get out there and kick some goblin butts!")
NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "5F11924D4B1E89005F8474898673595D", "Your assistance is much appreciated.")
NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "2797DF064C823FA5A6D8B49CB6931B73", "We could really use your help around here.")
NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "0394EC7A4618A7B160F011AADA1130BC", "Hey there.")

NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "556C94BD4505BCEBC088BE9F828F4E74", "Yapper helps smelly humens. Humens smashing goblin land. Yapper left stuff in Yapper’s cave when he join humens.\r\n\r\nYou get Yapper’s stuff if you want Yapper to help, yes?")
NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "C26E4B9B4B5EF8908D071D843EAF7F87", "Yes! Yes! You find Yapper’s things! You not as smelly as other humens. Where Yapper’s Favorite Fork? What you mean too dangerous?")

NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "2A3306244FFC9E1D1BA891981BE6FF13", "I'm sure you've heard the rumors… yes, I talked my way into coming along on this trip so I could find my father.

His name is Zephoras (I know). He's an emberologist, researching lost forms of ember for the university. He came on an expedition here early last year, but no one from his group returned…

The general won't let me leave the outpost. Could you please search the battlefield for me?")

NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "5BDE06CD4C3DFFBF00F99DA4374DBDD9", "What? He wasn't there? I guess I shouldn't have gotten my hopes up. Thank you for looking.

This amulet… it's the same as the necklace he gave me when I entered the university. This has to be his.

Please, I need to study it.")

NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "E1F4EFCD4E956E48C27AD68BDA3EE2B1", "Who’s that?! Oh, it’s just you.

You heard the story of the beast from the well of shadows, right? On a dark night just like this, a vanquisher put down a whole mess of undead. When he finished, something emerged from that well over there. Something dark and evil — right here in the Haunted Cemetery.

That can’t be true, right?")

NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "0191A4C642DA4AEDFC197FBE48CC9DD5", "You mean that thing was real? I thought that was just a story that Astern told the recruits ‘cause he likes to watch them wet themselves.\r\n\r\nNicely done. You deserve this.")

NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "843500504654CC3F691AAF87ACA67CE4", "It’s time for action, adventurer.

My eyes in the forest report that some important gob chieftain is assembling a war council. This is our chance to hit them all in one place.

Get to Gobtown, eliminate the council and find the chieftain and kill him.")

NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "59BD29FA48233EBD8D7973BEA84C792F", "Well done. You’ve weakened the goblins by striking at their leaders. Now they\'ll be even more inept and chaotic than before.\r\nLet’s see if we can tell the difference...")

NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "9805315A496903D5780BAF94BD7C3CF1", "The stone at the center of this pendant, it\'s ember, but like no ember I\'ve ever seen.\r\nIt\'s inert, but I think it may be Earth ember… I need more samples.")

NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "2AB895714CBCEB29ACA4759DD3ACC1D9", "That should be enough. It must be Earth ember. But why is it inert? Why did my father leave the necklace behind? I have to study this. Thank you.")

NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "039DACCD4E3E1BD884BE249E72D5FF38", "You wanna know where goblins keep their best weapons? Heh, Yapper knows!

Yapper told chief Pyro it dumb to keep ‘em all in one place.

You go to River Run. There’s a cave we call the Cave of Boom. It full of goblin weapons!")

NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "D60A0F644E575E2ED22BAE93CFCBA4D7", "Nice hit! I heard that one all the way over here.

Taking out the goblin leaders and their weapon stockpiles should weaken those gobs.

We're getting close to finally clearing the island.")
NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "503E20A84D9999133DBFD4AE16AC1D6E", "Are you ready for what\'s up ahead?")
NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "525AE30041F8EFD56629D899F2DA9025", "Are you prepared for what\'s ahead?")
NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "4148F4AB4EAB3291A28F67806ACEFB35", "I\'m not convinced that you\'re ready for the goblin incursion.")
NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "3D864DB045DC88002B2CA490A296B76E", "You\'ve proven yourself to be quite the hero! I salute you.")
NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "4B2910814D6839E427B216AD8A699CE6", "Hold it right there. Before you head deep into goblin country, you\'ll need to deal with the situation in the goblin villages.")
NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "936CE8114BD02FC554A4549963EB7935", "What? You haven\'t had enough? Well, it\'s your funeral.")
NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "651E703D47677CCE1380F79E98CCDEE0", "I\'m sure you know the drill by now. Come back when you\'ve dealt with the goblin menace in the Gobstomp Stronghold.")
NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "AE30E0744F1D3B610AC80DB5D635EC68", "I could tell you that I\'m impressed, but I won\'t.")
NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "7917E07B44DF894105055AA71B938FF7", "Well, be safe out there. There\'s some kind of lake ahead, crawling with goblins. I wonder if they swim?")
NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "CF5140A44E7DA0EBFDCF6D92650D9BE5", "I have no idea what a \"pig fish\" is, but I bet you can find some in Lake Gobdunk.")
NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "F33E67E34481093BF71F958A89A5A321", "If you think Lake Gobdunk is dangerous, wait until you see River Run!")
NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "D08C119A4B06F21B3CF7EDB49D2E2B20", "Be careful out there.")
NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "C636909D4A816086699D27B75B2E78EE", "Stock up on poison gear if you want to survive the Polluted Plateau.")
NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "3E7DD0AF4AA2042D0C2C19AA07C7395B", "Don\'t be so concerned about my methods. I\'m simply redistributing the wealth. Here, take this bundle and move along.")
NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "C068C53244C848C538F045A70C99B5F5", "Another freeloader, huh? I\'m not one to judge.")
NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "61E8B88E4A667BBDA4ACA0896D8DE2DE", "Sometimes, you\'ve got to just help yourself.")
NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "01D76DBD4C3295C0C7DFAFB0F3FE4B04", "Quit staring. I\'m not getting any prettier.")
NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "9660913D435F4C3F056C57980CC447D0", "Don\'t you have some place to be?")
NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "3BB270DB4480890C1AE5C8B43DDD33DE", "No more handouts for you. Go away.")

NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "4D0910054F764CCF38A6EB9B30CC9315", "Do you ever stop to think? What are these gobs doing with all the ore and ember they’re mining? They\'re not using all of it, so where does it go?\r\n\r\nIf you ask me, I think they’re selling it on the black market. I need you to bring me some samples of their higher quality stone and get some evidence of where it\'s going.")

NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "32EE47AA4096BCDB29C8CE842372010D", "I knew it! This invoice is from the Blood Legion, a merc company operating out of the Kalacama Desert. Those shipments were bound for mercs known for raiding Imperial camps. Good work!")

NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "1739A7A64976A5CBB9891E9915108144", "Okay, sure it may seem like it's going to take a while to make all those planks.

No, of course we don't expect you to stand around and wait. Why don't you fight something?

Ugh. Fine, this was laying around. See if you can use it to make your upgrades. Never say I didn't give you anything.")

NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "044B7D5B4372D4C34566B5BF29F83690", "Better watch out for those flesh-eating <span color=\"#FFD700\">Mossrats</>! It\'s the kind of vermin that will eat through just about anything--and anyone! Maybe you can help me lure the infamous <span color=\"#FFD700\">Carrion Killer</> out of its hideout and get this rodent problem under control. Wuddaya say, pal?")
NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "0368C5D14B4AC846E527D9A10875BC5D", "Yapper... hungry... you mebbee... TASTY?!")
NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "0B527E6B4F3916493C874D84E844A0F1", "Come closer humen... Yapper hungers!")
NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "0AD7A924489DF1AE66BAAA8B68746151", "Yapper free self. Tell goblins. Take humens. Feast. Mmm.")
NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "672FC0BB46B35C9285A9E9AE4D74ED9D", "Wat? Yapper not hiding things. You trust Yapper, yes?")
NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "25FCB91546B8815FEFEAB7B75C7D0245", "You bring pet? Feed Yapper?")
NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "F486D887495DCC8F631BCE9DCC0C2B64", "MINE!")
NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "82E1A53D40EFE4B8FAD1D8A6F7DDC46C", "Grrrr...")
NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "4C2D1477414834883B7B308C943F615C", "Yapper tell you! Yapper tell you!")
NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "F7EE5244483901F92607BC82C0925A66", "Yapper a good lil\' goblin, yes he is!")
NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "4CE14753413984004FE749B48ACB553A", "Yapper help humans, they feed, yes?")
NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "1F70153242EFB579459FFC8CF0C88048", "Yes, yapper knows. Yapper good helper!")
NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "BDF3D81A46C6171FDEC6E8801F575FDF", "You have treats for Yapper?")
NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "2BCF44C74E8454CA5AF5CE8EDBE92D4E", "No need to be so tasty er… hasty. Yes. Hasty.")
NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "D26458BF42002A6CBBBFE6A454FD2A29", "Yapper can help. If not so hungry…")
NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "04E7F5B547FDB8CA9D18159A427A23FD", "Yapper can have dragonling snack?")
NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "727600264FA7CEB0DF569CB6F7EDF076", "Ow! No poking Yapper!")
NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "1E9DE2D1464AB7334759BA87930DEF0C", "Yapper not forget what you do to Yapper. Yapper remember.")
NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "215947FD4911CB3861B523B079BC61EC", "You hit hard. Yapper not hit hard, but Yapper sneeeaky.")
NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "D27BF85F47245A9623CCCCA2912B6D7B", "Nothing to see here, move along.")
NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "4FED42D54F82B168FF85F08E12519873", "I\'d offer you some life advice, but I have none.")
NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "6C65125544BE3A86F88277A0A1989F9A", "General Graye stationed me here, probably as some form of punishment.")
NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "C75380634EB6A7A6D4AFEA813218A29C", "Yes, I\'m still here. What do you want?")
NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "CEC3AB1843F189489C084691E5C2D118", "Nice place you\'ve got here.")
NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "9A6C29574F323116D8BD389EE7FDBFDA", "Don\'t mind me as I continue to stand here and watch you work.")
NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "E156518D4E47D4D57D1427A66B038FA3", "I have direct orders to supervise and not interfere.")

NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "E984CB1C49E65CE9D5CFDB81AD0CE518", "Ever since the nearby infestation of the Hyvid, the natural flora that grows in the area has become increasingly scarce. If you can collect enough spores scattered throughout the Polluted Plateau, I’ll be able to preserve this endangered plant life that’s integral to our everyday recipes.")
NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "F67BE597404DB9E614A929A1DC16867B", "Aa-choo! Oh dear, I think I may be allergic. Thanks for--ACHOO!--collecting the spores for me.")

NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "1E6DD99346A63D3F62A848A052DDD5AD", "I have reports from our Chief Imperial Guard that the outskirts of our northern encampments have been overrun by the Hyvid. Conditions are critical, and I need you to escort any of our injured guards to safety. I’m sending out reinforcements as soon as possible.")
NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "B4BB77154C61DB576C83D5BF093DBDA4", "We were outnumbered... Tell the general that it\'s been an honor...")
NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "52B224564C5EF1D33F66869E9DA0654B", "I had a bad feeling about this. The chief\'s brave deeds won\'t be forgotten.")

NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "AF03FA6642268F2E11CB83A42D639C14", "I was afraid that we’d be too late to save them. We’ve already lost too many scouts to this menace. Find and eliminate this predator once and for all.")

NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "F358E05746D7D1E812A58DAB78D3D0BF", "Hey there, I know you, don’t I? Tell ya a secret… these mean lil’ buggers are high in protein, so why let them go to waste? Everything’s a lil’ bit poisonous to one creature or another. It’s all about moderation. Look, my mug is empty. Bring me some bug juice and you won’t regret it. That’s a promise.")
NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "4C5378D94175D4F64D30F3834FA15278", "Woo! That really packs a punch. I knew I could count on you.")
NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "26080C114D19E255A84D8287EE6E45D8", "We lost some important supplies while scouting around in the Abandoned Cavern. Do you think you can help us out?")
NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "09FA3A1E473B764BBC67489102D89655", "I hope it\'s not too late to retrieve our lost supplies from the Abandoned Cavern.")
NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "4D59913E41B3521612681F989A82C427", "Glad you\'re here. Our supplies were at a critical low. Those little buggers are really a nuisance, aren\'t they?")

NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "0FD44BC74241AA7B668970984EE2DBF2", "There’s a place nearby where the Hyvid don’t go--the Forsaken Hollow--and you’d think that it’d be a good thing, but the problem is that it’s full of the undead! Perhaps that’s enough to ward anyone away from that place. Maybe you’ll be able to fashion a weapon out of those old bones that’ll help scare the Hyvid swarm away. Seems risky, but worth a try?")
NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "586BC0CF4FF65BF6AB1D30BB5F475AD1", "Have you already rid the Forsaken Hollow of the undead?")

NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "DF24119A4BC9260AAD7994A3CE263F26", "We’ve got to take care of this Netherim incursion before they reach the encampment. Our imperial scouts reported Netherim rifts appearing among a Hyvid cave. Time is of the essence!")
NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "863DE38D460D2AEB656C0EB5A8E72B0D", "We need you to close the Netherim Rifts from the Nether Nook.")
NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "C23B95E2453D1D29C0DB7396C52C4916", "Those who have ventured deep within the Trampled Thicket have never returned. Take caution and be prepared with reinforcements.")

NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "6D3AD0344FB94325BFE8F6A82F87AFFC", "The Trampled Thicket can be found within the Infested Forest. Once you\'re in the Trampled Thicket, look for a path into the Ravaged Ravine when you\'re ready to face Psora.")

NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "44668A2A4EC8CAB16B77D7B8C05E503A", "This job is hazardous to my health. I narrowly escaped the geysers on my way over here, and now I need to really watch where I step. The acidic pools will eat right through you! You’ll have to be careful not to get knocked into one. Don’t say I didn’t warn you.")
NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "99760FA24384B1727A6FCB9C2B36B26E", "Will humen help find friend? Friend last seen in Maggot Mire. Bring back for Yapper, yes?")
NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "93CBD14F4AAE9176E180789423EF7A13", "Yapper friend dead? Yapper no need for dead things. Grawr!")

NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "BADFBA824EE9EA1DA56229B1678D1FF0", "Hyvid larvae are nasty lil’ critters, aren’t they? Occasionally, you can find some underdeveloped larvae that aren’t as vicious. They happen to be a delicacy if you can believe that.")

NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "4D3A51EF442E26C385A762BAAA7BFD34", "It use to be safe to venture into the Infested Cave, but the Hyvid has since taken residence in the one place that grows a special fungus that I need for spellcasting. Since you’re no stranger to spelunking by now, would you mind picking a few along the way?")
NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "393BD3C34FD0A707438DB4B78F2B73CF", "Thanks! I can always count on you to deliver.")

NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "FEB5257D43E9FCB1D88140934B110679", "I’m told you’ve gotten pretty good at pest control, so I’m sending you out for another assignment. Go to the The Shady Retreat and work your magic.")

NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "E5F634014CD975A10C278F84A4808171", "Strong Hyvid monsters are preventing us from getting any the closer to the Hyvid Citadel, and we’re simply no match for them. If you can clear a safe path, we may be able to regroup at Defended Passage.")

NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "E25FF737425138B2716A02AEC78ED900", "We haven’t heard from our troops for days and that’s never a good sign. I fear that they’ve been captured and imprisoned--or worse--eaten alive. You seem like a brave one with plenty of time to spare. Think you can venture into Swamp Cave and be a hero?")

NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "7428A36B40777BB6EEAB50B72081AA6B", "Long ago, the fallen Dwarven empire set up pumping stations run by Dwarven automata to extract the poison pooling in the area. The Dwarven Custodians continue to mindlessly guard it to this day. I suspect that they\'re not completely immune to the poison that\'s corrupted these lands.")

NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "9C6F51D546F4DDEA390516BAA5A7D722", "I’ve got a mild case of odontophobia, so it’s best that I stay away from those Netherlings, but if you happen to find any nether essence, I could really use a new batch.")

NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "B14D2AA443CDBFBEE6538BB3AE46A73F", "The Hyvid most certainly has a queen who is well protected in their hive, and your experience with the Hyvid colony makes you our best hope for clearing out this infestation. I trust that you can take care of it.")
NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "C87FB3F341DCA65882AD19A14D457D54", "I\'m afraid that we\'ve squashed one problem, only to reveal another. Speak to Zaya next.")

NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "871F0A1946CB4A7093DD3EB66C1A7ADA", "One of our scouts managed to draft a map of the Hyvid Capital, but was lost in transit. Can you help us retrieve it? He was last seen in Hyvid Forest.")

NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "9DE61A1D49C865572095068957856525", "Is this a map of the new Hyvid Capital? Our scouts risked a lot for this. Let\'s make sure that we have a plan of attack before risking more lives.")
NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "1FFF14A7406A164EF0371D9FA39D7078", "You’ve got to help me. The General is never trusting me with the armory keys again! It’s got to be around here somewhere...")
NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "CBCD3BF6488F8783940AB0ACB624FA74", "Well, we do have spare armory keys for the very same reason that someone keeps losing them. Thanks, anyway.")

NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "179A4CDF452D418F86225FBDCA6E4A44", "There was an awful buzz--and not just the usual kind from these Hyvid--in the general direction of Hyvid Grounds. I think it may be attracting more Hyvid into the area. Can you confirm the source and put a stop to it?")
NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "A0A32D4E4A6D5E3B0390F8A575DDD649", "Ember Beacons? Is that what\'s been driving the Hyvid crazy? I\'ll have our Imperial Investigators keep an eye out for these.")

NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "34E9A0A542E8442B1CC2DD8593A9B09D", "Of course, when the queen dies, a new one takes its place. Hyvid can be so predictable. Yet… they seem to have relocated their new queen further into their Hyvid capital, which seems rather unusual. This calls for an investigation. Let me know what you find.")

NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "086B8EE148C4014355A80E801DC70D41", "Many of the walking dead you see here are men from the last invasion of this land. We don’t know why they’ve risen again, but we hope you can put some of them to rest.")

NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "B261A7394FF43617F40C2CAF74868AAE", "Our caravans keep being raided. Go into the goblin territories and destroy anything you can. Better to burn it than leave it to the enemy.")

NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "AFA6576E42E12062CD65358945A35A69", "Dast was a Captain of the guard during our last invasion. We thought him lost, but have heard rumors he still \"lives,\" only now as a leader of creatures of the night. This cannot stand.")

NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "D4BB4C264FD928813479E48A800C989E", "Goblins killed my family, my brother’s family, and someone from just about every one of the soldier’s you see here’s families. Let’s try and even out the score a little.")

NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "B45078A64EF4643DBF90558ACFA87674", "Legions of Imperial soldiers have fallen to the goblins, their bodies often consumed or treated as prizes. The least we can do is recover their tags and bring them home to their families to let them know they weren\'t killed in vain.")

NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "87390C254D90C748CD4FFFA74A7155A1", "While our soldiers are brave, they continue to fall to goblin-trained beasts. Take out their trainer and kill the monsters protecting him.")

NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "69B20D30465DBEE947DA0E8C458D0AB4", "Goblins are easy enough to kill, but we’re being overwhelmed by their shamans who keep bringing them back. We’ve tracked down a particularly pesty one and want you to make sure he never returns.")

NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "553728A34487679788E55997539134A9", "The Imperial Academy is interested in developing tools that will mask our soldiers from the Hyvid. Slay the beasts, collect a variety of pheromonal glands, and then bring them to me.\r\n\r\nOne quick note though: the strange metamorphosis the Hyvid Guardians cause in the other Hyvid renders their organs unstable, so those Hyvid won\'t produce usable glands.")

NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "0038634D4EBD344DAF8D9FB85A2271F2", "Even the soldiers who make it back to camp after fighting the Hyvid often die to poison. The Empire wants to see if our alchemists can come up with a way to immunize our troops to poison, but for that we’ll need a concentrated sample.")

NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "AE263EE149FD587472DCF2845DA72918", "The ‘Vid can transform from grubs to soldiers in moments, and we believe it’s because of the hormonal secretion of their Guardians. We sent in a scouting party to study a big nasty one, but they had to pull out when they swarmed. Go through the portal I\'ll open, clear the area of all hostiles, and slay the guardian leader so we can study the remains.")

NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "FD0396F44289DD5B7D67ECACBA736536", "Hyvid larvae are nasty little things, but they turn even nastier when they grow up. Go out there and see to it that they don’t. Better yet, keep ‘em from hatching by squashing the Egg Pods.")
NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "D5DB617D4E6CB17250A6EEB3471D5037", "Thanks for doing this. The Empire appreciates your service, as do the families of those who fell against the ravenous goblin tide.")
NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "87AC079044D4E39A14273CBA5A4E102A", "These are...gross, but absolutely necessary for the future of our success here. Take these rewards for your trouble, frontierlander.")

NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "9AF5AA8C45AAC9EDB2443F8EB16968CC", "Hand that over very carefully. As I understand it just one drop of that stuff could kill you. Oh, did I forget to mention that part? Well, the past is the past and you\'ve done well. Thanks, frontierlander.")

NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "F4E37130425136199752A18F4F2C59CD", "You\'ve proven valuable to this invasion, but we know the hardest parts are yet to come. Improve your fort and your skills to be ready for the challenges ahead.")
NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "E32155444B667CB751B9C09C98B3B58F", "Feel stronger, right? No? Well, you’re still in a better place than you were when I first met you. Take this for your troubles.")

NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "2EB56C884C8A1BD6025585A0B7F93DE5", "The Empire thanks you for your service with more ways to serve. Completing these goals will help ensure success in our mission here and give you the means to make your fort a little more livable.")

NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "AB46935E426853ADB48C6DB82E7C3119", "Wait, you\'re done...already? Well, next time we might just have to give you a bit more to do, eh? Thanks for your service, take this.")

NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "2965FCF64DF717F0760518A5E129E406", "Our initial invasion is successful, but we know the Netherim are influencing the actions of the goblins and hyvid. Worse still, we believe one of our own is providing intelligence to the enemy. Help us with our investigation and take out some enemies. To begin we need you to kill goblins...")

NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "0C0D24A84D167A6A9EFA5B83B6E0B42E", "The goblins are reeling, but their leader has started to make moves. Go and slay the big goblin called Wideload. Clear out his dungeon so our investigators can check it out for leads.")
NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "F68D9B77493EE5B259C631BFBD8D68DE", "Now that the cave is clear we’ll send in a team to investigate the area for evidence. Here’s the next area I need you to safe guard.")

NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "0C83FCBD427A4226174432988886D8B0", "Our team from the first dungeon turned up clues that point us towards collusion between the goblins and the bugs. Yapper denies it, of course. We need you to take out some grubs to see if you can draw out one of their more important hive members.")

NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "1634DB19453C195768A90BB36F6CCE85", "Great. I’ve just received word that the bugs are planning on attacking a nearby fort in conjunction with the goblins. This is bad. We need you to stop the bug assault before it happens by culling their numbers and destroying their hive leader.")

NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "77926B6541F73100D613BCAA6A242DDE", "Good work. We still haven’t figured out who is coordinating these attacks, but you’ve bought our people plenty of time to investigate. All I can tell you for now is that it appears a very strong Netherim is in charge.")

NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "5C04E72148A9A9A33A98FDA81BAE2C7F", "Well hello! You\'ve… uh, come at an awkward time. We\'ve got our hands full with the goblins. Usually, we can handle \'em, but this time, they got some crazy big goblin. We\'ve been callin\' him <span color=\"#FFD700\">Wideload</>. Before we can take his big ol\' keister out, we gotta defend the outpost.\r\n\r\nHead up there and clear those goblins out!")
NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "28E3F60B466F7600D5E143A547D6E1D9", "Wha? No, I gotta stay here… to guard the ships.")
NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "11A236574F5F636DAEF293954F7F4423", "You\'ve got this. I\'d help, but… my knee.")
NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "8C3049754D7FD1B73C373187D3301862", "What, are ya chicken?")

NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "79D2E3C8471804EC7098D395CE7FB2F1", "Thanks for the help! Ever since the one they call <span color="#FFD700">Wideload</> arrived, they’ve been getting the better of us out in the battlefields. The local goblins are growing increasingly bold.

You must be here for the Frontiers program. Well, we're serious about supporting you hero types. You make a home out here in the frontier and we'll be here for supplies and information.
I've got a portal scroll somewhere here for you.

Ah, yes. This will take you to your very own fort. Sgt. Klive should already be there. He'll introduce you to your fort, but then you come see me, if you want some work.")
NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "0D2E25D949699D7ED635CFB70D4F17B0", "Thanks, this should be plenty of Nether Essence for now.")
NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "5A59FDE44E2E0A8F079A72B5B9B09165", "I\'d better check that tougher gob. He doesn\'t seem quite dead…")
NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "313EA5414BE7EF5DBA39038EC6809451", "On behalf of the Empire, thanks again for your help.")
NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "49ECD40D4266C6A0FE123BBC856C99CD", "What are you waiting for? You going to claim your fort, or what?")

NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "3779EE0844A34E1639241B88EA1DD12A", "Heya, frontierlander! As one of the first arrivals here in the frontier, I've been given special permission to grant you a welcome package. Y'know, to say thanks for everything you do?

It's got great stuff for your fort. You should really get… Oh, no. Not these. These are just floor models.

Head straight to your fort. They're already there, you just have to pick a good spot for 'em!")

NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "0538374F46C1FE9A5F03479441427B5F", "Oh no you don\'t. Beyond here is what we call Bogwood Hollow, on account of all the swampy, poisonous pools in there. You\'ll have to complete the work you\'ve been given first, before I can let you in here.")
NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "E68D102D4A7D5C8FA228F5A2B0F340BF", "Sorry, if you want to delve deep into the Acrid Plains, you\'ll have to complete the rest of your goals before I can allow you in.")

NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "877F045E4332720D6785158FDA5CF8E3", "We\'re getting so deep into the Hyvid territory here. You sure you want to go into the Wastelands? Well, you still have more to do to prove yourself qualified.")

NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "C79B04E74926C0CEBEEC1181C7B7C3EB", "I know, I know. You must be getting tired of this by now, but look, I\'m just doing my job here. If you want to go into the Hyvid Habitat, then yes, there are still just a few more things you have to do…")

NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "A0B5652D4EE7FD26266A8EBBBA96ADA6", "I generally think it’s better to be indoors by nightfall, but we need someone stu...pendously awesome to go out and slay the undead hordes and other particularly evil things.")
NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "856133C04B6DF7937BCB1A8DF6D45856", "Oh, hey, you made it! I mean, of COURSE you made it. The Empire appreciates your service and offers you this reward.")

NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "244410F1404B1A00FD7B3FBF3B96D2F0", "Hey there. We don't like to think about it all the time, but the netherim are always waiting to rip their way into our world.

The bad news is, I think we've found a tear. My netherim wards are starting to fail, but I think I've pinpointed where the netherim disturbance is located.

I need you to find the source of the netherim, some kind of stable portal and find a way to shut it down.")

NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "624BFB5A49E674359F7B57944F59D10E", "You did it!

Now that you've sealed the Netherim rift, I'll be able to reform my wards protecting this place.

It sounds like that Varkenin was being corrupted by the Netherim, so I'm glad you were able to stop him in time.

This won't stop the Netherim for very long, but it'll at least give us a break.")
NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "3F35717B4250FD726EA95380AFDCE9E1", "Find and speak to Kenik for your next assignment.")

NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "41F74EA34423C3321F9B308304253DF6", "Ah, look brother. I’ve had a recent string of, uh bad luck. Sometimes bad things happen to good people, y’know? But this, this is somethin’ different! See, this weirdo mage guy had us steal this chest of gold from a haunted cavern. You know, standard stuff. Now Jackdaw, my partner on this job, he says this treasure had a curse. Now he ends up dead and I can’t catch a break. I need ya to put this gold back. And, y’know, get me some more. Whaddya say?")
NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "AC2FB84F4E08E45AE016AFB4F0B3F370", "The Phix the Blacksmith can forge you a weapon, but first, I\'ll need you to collect a few supplies.")

NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "3D9F37184D876615333BB997F43FCA8C", "Those Goblin pyromaniacs have been wrecklessly setting everything near town on fire. The dry bramble has become a huge fire hazard to the camps, and we could really use your help in clearing them out.")
NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "9B5651F444A4020F1E09AEB516E9DD26", "Thanks, we can safely burn all of these bramble from here.")

NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "CA1451654453B47C64CD07B80EC82B12", "Zaya\'s always in need of strange and unusual ingredients, and she\'s provided a list of things for you to collect from River Run. Go there and see what you can find.")
NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "EA49488C4339ECD42ECE58AF136BDEC6", "Oh, thanks! These will be perfect for my homemade remedies.")

NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "B18340B447E182DA2F626D918E314F59", "Word has it that there are Automata patrolling the Deforested Land, as if it\'s not enough that the Hyvid are already destroying the ecosystem.")

NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "22980C794A62B647ED27E8B2DBADE740", "They say that imitation is the highest form of flattery, but these monsters are making a literal mimicry of things. Destroy any mimics that you find out in the field and report back to me.")
NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "B8378B334F2AB6091991339D046260B6", "Well done. Often imitated, never duplicated, right?")
NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "2482EEA541316468E0D56992253CA7F1", "Report to Officer Gadfly for your next task.")

NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "AA480E4845B0FCB46B6F738261D1B06C", "Know anything about the Boarmen? Our troops have sighted one such beast roaming the outskirts of the forest. If you can lure the beast away from the campsites, perhaps we can find it a new home for it while it\'s knocked out. The Goblins tend to carry a certain kind of bait that you can use to set a trap. Well, you know what to do next.")

NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "699EC3164A775DCC1A4B15BE53D38A43", "Head to Deadgob Falls and locate the Goblin trading boat. Confiscate their stolen supplies and return them to Officer Hobbs in the Lakeside Clearing.")
NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "9E43242C46B43E3E4DDF3E8F7D03B147", "Thank you for your service.")

NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "2E9124D045FD34F8DCAAA6930F620802", "We sent [NPC] to deliver some important messages, but [NPC] hasn\'t reported back from duty after venturing into the Haunted Cemetary. Now, I\'m not generally superstitious, but with a name like that, we should have known better.")

NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "DA83B4C84EFA9CBAC45AAA866A35A4CE", "I\'ve got a bit of a scavenger hunt for you. Goblin Gunners have been stealing our firing pins and hiding them under piles of rocks. We stumbled upon this odd habit when one of our troops knocked over a stone pile. Get to them before they become worm food.")

NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "EB3ED70D4782B35243791C8789CD0CFE", "Hiding things under a pile of rocks is not the most subtle way of keeping things hidden, but at least it makes our job a little easier, right? Wait, what? Y--you collected the grubs, too? I didn\'t ask for this, but I bet Zaya will be able to find some use out of these.")
NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "6239DA024649CA536CE29FBDD844CD24", "Oh, are these for me? Uh, thanks for the grubs... You\'re a little weird, but I like you.")

NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "0BB28CFD4B8B42112178639DEB9DB743", "There are corrupted ember crystals that seem to sprout overnight throughout the Hyvid Frontier. The Hyvid seems to have formed a symbiotic relationship with them, using them to strengthen their exoskeletons. Destroy any Hyvid Armor Crystals that you find and bring back fragments for further research.")
NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "9AE2DA414C3635464B5E01A9F4BCFDFD", "Thanks, this should be plenty.")

NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "6976110948F516A27C12A992A93F76B8", "Zaya just handed me a list of things that are short in supply for the outpost, so I guess you are going to be our resupplier today. Lucky you.")
NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "8C9E3BC74A8CB2B6E535C3AD5B337ED3", "This is perfect! It\'s just what I--I mean--we needed.")

NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "D13F5380498F13BB83C5C3AE3F43759F", "We\'ve placed a few traps to capture some of the Hyvid Larvae, but we need someone to retrieve them. We sent some scouts out to look for them, but they haven\'t reported back yet. This may end up being a search and rescue mission. Are you up for it?")

NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "852064E046F2AF23DF99EAB8D6A49868", "Goblins are raising an army of beasts led by the one they call, \"Dogjockey\". Drive them out of their hiding place and take down their leader.")

NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "BF6499244D272A69B5DB368A9E09543A", "I\'ve heard that you\'re the one to talk to about tracking down beasts. If what I\'ve been told is true, then I\'ve got the perfect task for you.")

NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "2BD098374794B5556547B28968221E62", "Goblin Brutes have employed a new method of coralling our troops into cages using their large wall-like shields. Confiscate shields from Goblin Brutes and try not to get knocked-out by any of them.")

NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "02E773D044DEC41FC718C8A1628707E8", "We\'ve had our eye on a particular target--one of the undead--who\'s been leading large waves of zombie invaders to our camps. See if you can invoke an appearance from none other than Eye-Gore himself. ")
NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "7F033E5844CA014A87E4FDBD41431E39", "Report to [NPC] in Bugswat Pass for your next assignment.")

NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "AA7473D64230CEA6619FF0B9BB6C7204", "Good, I\'ve been waiting for you. Within the Hyvid Tunnels, there is a mean lil\' bugger that has taken the lives of several members of our guard. Get inside and clear a safe path, then take out Swyrt, the Stinger. But before you go, could you do me a favor and find my bug swatter? I must have dropped it somewhere nearby.")
NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "47C5277844A98A318F035AB6D3C4A9E3", "Thanks, this should help with the creepy crawlies.")

NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "9347631F4242648BD349E081988AF37C", "You never want to be under-prepared in the new frontier. Gather more supplies of Ash Logs and Sandstone Rocks., then report to [NPC] for your next task.")

NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "C1014349495F82AE18486DA5B5402B8C", "I don\'t know much about the disgusting concoctions that our researchers have been brewing up, but they are suppose to counter some of the negative effects inlficted upon our troops. Talk to the Imperial Pest Control Researcher in the Polluted Plateau for your next assignment.")

NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "317D7A3A4BDBFD8869EF8FA1ADEF466E", "We\'ve been studying the fauna and flora of the Hyvid frontier for quite some time, and have discovered that small doses of a little of this and that has beneficial effects on our patients. Unfortunately, it\'s not so easy to extract all of the ingredients. Are you up for the challenge?")
NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "14107C9C43E349A67EF65E8FDD8A1663", "I knew we could count on you.")

NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "EDF9F5E24926AA1F17A7588EB9E462C6", "After you\'ve driven the goblins out of the Den of Upheaval, they\'ve managed to take over the cave all over again. Not only that, but they\'ve also grown in numbers throughout the area. ")

NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "F1006B394967987C4C47889145E5257F", "I\'m sending you out to the Polluted Plateau to do a bit of pest control. Locate every cave or forest in the area and clear out as many Hyvid as you can.")

NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "5F71E3344581BEAA8FD7C0B8922382F4", "The Gobs are digging deep into the earth and robbing graves throughout the Imperial Battlefield. Locate these areas and drive them out before they cause any more damage.")

NSLOCTEXT("DialogueTable", "A16C21EB430559F44E07EFA05EF34FA4", "From what we\'ve observed, the Hyvid life cycle is short, but their ability to rapidly metamorphosize from an egg to adult form is beyond anything that I\'ve ever seen. Go into the Infested Forest and clear them out of their various breeding grounds before the situation gets out of control.")
